name: Ryan Gosling
description:
Info about the person:

Ryan Gosling is a Canadian actor. Prominent in both independent film and major studio features of varying genres, his films have accrued a worldwide box office gross of over 1.9 billion USD. He has received various accolades, including a Golden Globe Award, and nominations for two Academy Awards and a BAFTA Award.

Note about the model:

This model was trained on a dataset of 145 images, I always try to add more images if their quality is good, and this model also shows good results in the DeepFace tests. You can find the dataset (txt and img) of this model here.

It's too hot on Civitai, feel free to get me a drink!
